axis=0 : Column-wise
axis=1 : Row-wise

Q11.Why can NumPy perform millions of operations faster than a Python loop?
NumPy uses optimized C code and vectorized operations.

Q12.What is Boolean Masking and why is it heavily used in Data Science?
Boolean Masking filters data using True/False conditions.

